Willie LEWIS, alias Willis Lewis, alias Walter Lewis, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 6104. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. March 14, 1931. R. A. Hendricks, of Miami, Fla., for appellant. W. P. Hughes, U. S. Atty., and Wm. A. Paisley, Asst. U. S. Atty., both of Jacksonville, Fla.

Before FOSTER, SIBLEY, and HUTCHESON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment in this ease is affirmed.
